Why AGPL-3.0 for PRAHARI
------------------------------------------------------------------------
AGPL-3.0 is the strongest free/open-source copyleft license. Because
PRAHARI is intended to be run as a networked service, the AGPL closes the
"SaaS loophole": anyone who deploys a modified version of PRAHARI over a
network must also make their modified source available to its users. This
protects the project's sovereign, open, and auditable ethos.

The full, canonical license text is published by the Free Software
Foundation at the URL above and is incorporated here by reference. A
verbatim copy of that text will be added to this file in the repository.
